数据，而不需要在每个级别显式地将 props 传递给所有组件。\r\n- Redux: 复杂应用全局状态管理可以使用Redux、Mobx等状态管理库，项目里一般使用React Redux或者RTK工具包。\r\n- Pub/Sub: 发布/订阅模式是一种通过事件来进行任意组件间通信的方法，和Vue里的事件总线原理一样。\r\n- Hooks里也可以通过useReducer和useContext来实现全局组件通信。","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/416/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/416/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}